<h3 class="endpoint">
    GET /api/v1/courses/:course_id/files
  </h3>
<h3 class="endpoint">
    GET /api/v1/users/:user_id/files
  </h3>
<h3 class="endpoint">
    GET /api/v1/groups/:group_id/files
  </h3>
<h3 class="endpoint">
    GET /api/v1/folders/:id/files
  </h3>
<p>Returns the paginated list of files for the folder or course.</p>
